Sentencas: The electrolyte material Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.92 (SDC) powders are synthesized by glycine nitrate processes and BaCe0.83Y0.17O3-delta (BCY) powders are synthesized by sol gel processes, respectively.
Titulo: Electrical properties of SDC-BCY composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Then SDC BCY composite electrolytes are prepared by mixing SDC and BCY.
Titulo: Electrical properties of SDC-BCY composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The SDC and BCY powders are mixed in the weight ratio of 95:5, 90:10 and 85:15 and named as 5395, SB90 and SB85, respectively.
Titulo: Electrical properties of SDC-BCY composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The electrical properties of SDC and SDC BCY composites are investigated.
Titulo: Electrical properties of SDC-BCY composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The experimental results show that SDC BCY composites exhibit the excellent conductivity and could significantly enhance the fuel cell performances.
Titulo: Electrical properties of SDC-BCY composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The behavior that SDC BCY composites display hybrid proton and oxygen ion conduction is substantiated.
Titulo: Electrical properties of SDC-BCY composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Among these electrolytes, the maximum power density reaches as high as 159 mW cm(-2) for the fuel cell based on SB90 composite electrolyte at 600 degrees C. Copyright (C) 2014, Hydrogen Energy Publications, LLC.
Titulo: Electrical properties of SDC-BCY composite electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell
